span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Necessities_for_becoming_an_orthopedic_surgeon\" title=\"Necessities for becoming an orthopedic surgeon\">Necessities for becoming an orthopedic surgeon<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Duties_of_an_Orthopedic_Doctor\" title=\"Duties of an Orthopedic Doctor\">Duties of an Orthopedic Doctor<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Suggestions_to_become_a_board_certified_orthopedic_surgeon\" title=\"Suggestions to become a board certified orthopedic surgeon\">Suggestions to become a board certified orthopedic surgeon<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Salaries_of_orthopedic_jobs\" title=\"Salaries of orthopedic jobs\">Salaries of orthopedic jobs<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Advantages_of_being_an_orthopedic_surgeons\" title=\"Advantages of being an orthopedic surgeons\">Advantages of being an orthopedic surgeons<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/#Disadvantages\" title=\"Disadvantages\">Disadvantages<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>The path of becoming a orthopedic surgeon is challenging and candidates for residency face competition. To boost your chances, we have a few tips to help you stand out and start your journey in below.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2273 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Beck-5-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"158\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030023\">Necessities for becoming an orthopedic surgeon<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030024\">Duties of an Orthopedic Doctor<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030025\">Suggestions to become a board certified orthopedic surgeon<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030026\">Salaries of orthopedic jobs<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030027\">Advantages of being an orthopedic surgeons<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83030028\">Disadvantages<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"necessities-for-becoming-an-orthopedic-surgeon\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Necessities_for_becoming_an_orthopedic_surgeon\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030023\"><\/a>Necessities for becoming an orthopedic surgeon<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2274 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/AOSM-Group--300x203.jpg\" alt=\"How to become Orthopedic Surgeon\" width=\"300\" height=\"203\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>To become an orthopedic surgeon the following is required:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Earn a bachelor\u2019s degree<\/li>\n<li>Pass the medical College Admission (MCAT)<\/li>\n<li>Complete medical school as DO or MD<\/li>\n<li>Complete fellowship<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong><em>A fellowship<\/em><\/strong> <strong><em>usually takes one to two years to complete and is where orthopedic surgeons study:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hand, foot, ankle, spine surgery<\/li>\n<li>Pediatric orthopedics<\/li>\n<li>Orthopedic oncology<\/li>\n<li>Reconstructive surgery<\/li>\n<li>Surgical sports medicine.<\/li>\n<li>Become board certified<\/li>\n<li>Complete residency.<\/li>\n<li>Earn national and<span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"http:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\/<\/a><\/span>or state license.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"duties-of-an-orthopedic-doctor\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Duties_of_an_Orthopedic_Doctor\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030024\"><\/a>Duties of an Orthopedic Doctor<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The good part of theirs day is spent in surgery and them also:<\/li>\n<li>Be on call to respond to emergencies like car accidents or trauma<\/li>\n<li>They consult patients<\/li>\n<li>As well as educating patients on their condition<\/li>\n<li>Order and interpret diagnostic tests like MRIs or X<a href=\"http:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">&#8211;<\/span><\/a>rays<\/li>\n<li>They carryout prescriptions of medication or post-surgical rehabilitation<\/li>\n<li>Account for bacterial or viral infections<\/li>\n<li>Address genetic conditions<\/li>\n<li>Completion of an accurate chart for each patient record<\/li>\n<li>Perform surgical techniques such as arthroscopy to diagnose joint issues or set broken bones.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"suggestions-to-become-a-board-certified-orthopedic-surgeon\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Suggestions_to_become_a_board_certified_orthopedic_surgeon\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030025\"><\/a>Suggestions to become a board certified orthopedic surgeon<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>Below are the helpful tips to achieve your dream goal.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Study science while in high school<\/li>\n<li>Earn high scores on MCAT and licensing exams<\/li>\n<li>Maintain stellar medical school grades<\/li>\n<li>Collect strong letters of recommendation<\/li>\n<li>Perform well in clinical rotations<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"salaries-of-orthopedic-jobs\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Salaries_of_orthopedic_jobs\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030026\"><\/a>Salaries of orthopedic jobs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><\/td>\n<td><strong><em>Annual Salary<\/em><\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"170\"><strong><em>Monthly Pay<\/em><\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Top Earners<\/td>\n<td>$400,000<\/td>\n<td width=\"170\">$33,333<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>75th Percentile<\/td>\n<td>$400<a href=\"http:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">,<\/span><\/a>000<\/td>\n<td width=\"170\">$33,333<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Average<\/td>\n<td>$386,333<\/td>\n<td width=\"170\">$32,194<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>25th Percentile<\/td>\n<td>$387,500<\/td>\n<td width=\"170\">$32,291<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2 id=\"advantages-of-being-an-orthopedic-surgeons\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Advantages_of_being_an_orthopedic_surgeons\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030027\"><\/a>Advantages of being an orthopedic surgeons<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>The benefits are outlined below: <\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dental insurance -60 percent<\/li>\n<li>Vision insurance -47 percent<\/li>\n<li>Retirement plan with employer match -55percent<\/li>\n<li>Paid time off -55 percent<\/li>\n<li>Health insurance -78 percent<\/li>\n<li>Professional liability coverage: 69 percent.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"disadvantages\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Disadvantages\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83030028\"><\/a>Disadvantages<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>8 cons of being a surgeon<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>High \u2013stress levels<\/li>\n<li>Impact on social life<\/li>\n<li>Exposure to malpractice suits<\/li>\n<li>Long hours and burnout<\/li>\n<li>Lots of education<\/li>\n<li>Negative environments<\/li>\n<li>Luxury schooling<\/li>\n<li>Risk of infection.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><em><strong>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <\/strong><\/em><\/span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><em><strong><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" title=\"How to become a Midwife in Canada\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-midwife-in-canada\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">How to become a Midwife in Canada<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to become Orthopedic Surgeon- Necessities for becoming an orthopedic surgeon, Duties, Advantages and Disadvantages. The path of&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2276,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[728],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2271"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2271"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2271\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2271"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2271"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2271"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w